{
  "texts": [
    "In fact, we believe that the true value of the workshop lies in the extended discussions between participants of different backgrounds that explored a wide range of complexities not easily done in more conventional formats.",
    "This was the motivation for the recordings capturing all participants and the whiteboard, with high-quality audio.",
    "This report does not do justice to the depth of the discussions.",
    "On the other hand, the recordings also reveal the limitations of the Forum.",
    "Given the small number of participants, the content is necessarily limited in its breadth and comprehensiveness, even though it was already narrowed to issues related to immunology."
  ]
}